{"id": "1665876314", "isEnabled": true, "objectTypeId": "0-3", "flowType": "WORKFLOW", "revisionId": "18", "name": "Bot Hook | Design", "description": "Sends SMS and email updates about the Site Survey phase to customers in Colorado managed by a specific project manager, then triggers a webhook and notifies an internal user.", "uuid": "Bot Hook | Design-1665876314", "createdAt": "2025-06-25T19:11:47.459Z", "updatedAt": "2026-02-20T17:58:28.667Z", "startActionId": "2", "nextAvailableActionId": "8", "actions": [{"actionId": "1", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "3"}, "fields": {"property_name": "project_status", "value": {"staticValue": "This is a {{ enrolled_object.project_type }} project worth a contract value of {{ enrolled_object.amount }}. The project stage is {{ enrolled_object.dealstage }}.\n\nThe sales consultant is {{ enrolled_object.hubspot_owner_id }}. \n\nThe project manager is {{ enrolled_object.project_manager }}. \n\nThis project is based out of our {{ enrolled_object.pb_location }} office. \n\nThe address for this job is {{ enrolled_object.address_line_1 }}, {{ enrolled_object.city }}, {{ enrolled_object.state }} {{ enrolled_object.postal_code }}.\n\nThe Authority Having Jurisdiction (AHJ) is {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_149304111.record_name }}. They take {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_149304111.permit_turnaround_average }} days to approve permits. \n\nThe utility company for this address is {{ enrolled_object.utility_company }}\n\nThe site survey status is {{ enrolled_object.site_survey_status }}.\n\nThe design approval status is{{ enrolled_object.layout_status }}.\n\nThe design & engineering status is {{ enrolled_object.design_status }}. \n\nThe permit status is {{ enrolled_object.permitting_status }}. The permit submission date is: {{ enrolled_object.permit_submit_date }}. The permit issued date is {{ enrolled_object.permit_completion_date }}. \n\nThe interconnection application status with the utility company is {{ enrolled_object.interconnection_status }}.\n\nThe construction status is {{ enrolled_object.install_status }}. \n\nThe inspection status is {{ enrolled_object.final_inspection_status }}. ", "type": "STATIC_VALUE"}}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "2", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-1", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "1"}, "fields": {"delta": "2", "time_unit": "MINUTES"}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "3", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "4"}, "fields": {"property_name": "design_approval_update___sms", "value": {"staticValue": "Hello, this is Olivia - Virtual Assistant with Photon Brothers. Your project is moving into the Design Approval phase, where our expert team will create an engineered design based on your home's specific layout and energy needs.\n\nThis phase typically takes about two weeks and once it\u2019s complete we will send it to you for review and approval before moving on to permitting.\n\nThanks again for choosing Photon Brothers - we\u2019re excited for your project and will be in contact soon regarding your finalized design.\n\nReply END to stop texts.", "type": "STATIC_VALUE"}}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "4", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "6"}, "fields": {"property_name": "design_approval_update___email", "value": {"staticValue": "Hello, this is Olivia - Virtual Assistant with Photon Brothers.\n\nYour Site Survey is complete and we\u2019re moving on to the Design Approval phase! Our team is now creating an engineered design based on your home\u2019s specific layout and energy needs.\n\nThis phase typically takes about two weeks and once it\u2019s complete we will send it to you for review and approval before moving on to permitting.\n\nThanks again for choosing Photon Brothers - we\u2019